subject: Re: Interim Assistance General Man
body:
Hello Donald,

Good morning to you too! I hope this message finds you well. 

I appreciate your efforts in reaching out to me regarding the trunk box. It's quite intriguing, I must say. However, before we proceed further, could you please provide more information about how this box came into your possession? Also, what exactly does it mean that my "was tagged family valuables"? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Marceline
